     FAJSPP60 IP  E                    DISK
     FAJSWP64 O   E                    DISK
     FAJSWP65 O   E                    DISK
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80J6KEHZ
     I                                        1   40J6KEIY
     I                                        5   60J6KEIM
     I                                        7   80J6KEID
      *
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           PHIZK   8
     C                     PARM           PRECD   7
     C                     PARM           PKENS   7
     C                     MOVE PHIZK     WHIZK   80
      *
     C                     ADD  1         WRECD   70
      *
     C           J6KEHZ    IFGT WHIZK
     C                     ADD  1         WKENS   70
     C                     WRITEAJSWP641
     C                     ELSE
     C                     WRITEAJSWP651
     C                     END
      *
     CLR                   MOVE WRECD     PRECD
     CLR                   MOVE WKENS     PKENS
